Blank expressions now graced the faces of the captive audience.  Dumb drooling, so eager and ready to obey.  

Two other figures stepped out on stage as the witch beckoned them to her.  "Now the real fun begins."

author: Ms. Mesmer
text:
"In this time and in this place, you lose yourself with quite a haste.  Your thoughts will fade, your will be mine, and you will serve till the end of time."

The sounds of the crowd began to dull, silence quickly dominating the room.

author: Ms. Mesmer
text:
... the curtains covering the large circular window in the back of the room parted, allowing moon light to flood the space.  

Holding her hand aloft, she smirked.  "Mustn't forget the magic words." 

Moonlight sparkled off the ring as the chant flowed over her lips.

author: Ms. Mesmer
text:
